hnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</placeName><date when="1897-07-20" n="01">20. 7. 1897</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1897-07-17_02">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, [17. oder 18. 7. 1897?]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1897-08-04_01">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 4. 8. 1897</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
